---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Foundation Install | Badmouth Digital" description="Your complete lead system. Built and running in under 30 days. $3,500 to build. $297/month to keep it running." currentPage="foundation-install">

    <!-- SECTION 1 — CONTEXT HEADER -->
    <section class="section section--hero surface-base noise-bg has-scanlines" style="position: relative; min-height: auto; padding-top: var(--space-24); padding-bottom: var(--space-12);">
        <div class="grid-page">
            <div class="col-content stack-4 text-center">
                <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-inline: auto;">
                    <span class="status-dot status-dot--live"></span>
                    <p class="t-eyebrow" style="margin: 0;">Layer 1: The Foundation</p>
                </div>
                <h1 class="t-display t-display--hero" style="margin-inline: auto;">
                    YOUR COMPLETE<br />
                    <span style="color: var(--color-brand);">LEAD SYSTEM.</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="t-body t-body--lg" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">
                    Built and running in under 30 days.
                </p>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 55ch;">
                    This is what every other marketing move depends on. Without it, ads leak money, SEO drives traffic to dead ends, and you're stuck playing whack-a-mole every day.
                </p>
                <a href="/see-the-system" class="btn btn--outline">See What's Included →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 2 — TIMELINE -->
    <section class="section section--padded surface-sunken">
        <div class="grid-page grid-gap-lg">
            <div class="col-full text-center stack-4">
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section" style="margin-inline: auto;">
                    INSTALLED IN <span class="t-accent t-flicker">UNDER 30 DAYS.</span>
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-full">
                <div class="inner-grid-3">
                    <div class="card stack-3" style="border-top: 3px solid var(--color-brand);">
                        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">
                            <span style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 2px 8px;">PHASE 01</span>
                            <span style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.6rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);">3–5 DAYS</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">AUDIT & MAPPING</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">We look at what you've got, map your services, find the holes, plan the build.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card stack-3" style="border-top: 3px solid var(--theme-accent-teal);">
                        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">
                            <span style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 2px 8px;">PHASE 02</span>
                            <span style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.6rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);">10–14 DAYS</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">BUILD</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Website, CRM, automations, tracking, reviews. Everything gets built and wired together.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card stack-3" style="border-top: 3px solid var(--theme-accent-yellow);">
                        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">
                            <span style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 2px 8px;">PHASE 03</span>
                            <span style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.6rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);">3–5 DAYS</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">TEST & LAUNCH</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">We test every automation and tracking point. Verify every lead path. Flip it live.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-full text-center">
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">
                    System goes live. Maintenance kicks in. You get back to work.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 3 — INVESTMENT -->
    <section class="section section--statement section--padded surface-base">
        <div class="grid-page grid-align-center grid-gap-lg">
            <div class="col-left-7 stack-4">
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section">
                    <span style="color: var(--color-brand);">$3,500</span> TO BUILD.<br />
                    <span style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal);">$297/MONTH</span> <span class="t-accent t-flicker">TO KEEP IT RUNNING.</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="max-width: 55ch;">
                    $3,500 covers the complete build. Website, CRM, automations, tracking, reviews, dashboard. Everything.
                </p>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="max-width: 55ch;">
                    $297/month covers maintenance. Automations glitch. Tracking drifts. Things break. Maintenance keeps it all running tight so you don't wake up wondering why the leads stopped.
                </p>
                <p class="t-body t-body--lg" style="max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">
                    If this helps you close two extra jobs a month, it pays for itself.
                </p>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="max-width: 55ch;">
                    This isn't a retainer. It's the cost of your business running right.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-right-5">
                <div class="retro-box retro-box--danger" style="padding: var(--space-6);">
                    <p class="t-body" style="color: var(--color-brand); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; font-size: 0.7rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">What you're actually comparing this to:</p>
                    <div class="stack-3">
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">✗ Receptionist you can't afford — $2,500–$3,500/mo</p>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">✗ One missed $4,000 job per week</p>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">✗ Reviews you're not getting</p>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">✗ Hours chasing follow-ups instead of working</p>
                    </div>
                    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 0, 51, 0.2); margin: var(--space-4) 0;" />
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm" style="color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">You're not buying a website. You're buying your time back and plugging the holes in your revenue.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 4 — WHO THIS IS FOR -->
    <section class="section section--padded surface-elevated">
        <div class="grid-page grid-align-center grid-gap-lg">
            <div class="col-left-7 stack-4">
                <p class="t-eyebrow">Who This Is For</p>
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section">
                    BUILT FOR BUSINESSES THAT<br />
                    <span class="t-accent t-flicker">ALREADY HAVE WORK COMING IN.</span>
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-right-5">
                <div class="card stack-3" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--theme-accent-teal);">
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm" style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal);">✓ You already get calls and leads (you just lose too many)</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm" style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal);">✓ You know what you offer and how you price it</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm" style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal);">✓ You can handle more work if it showed up</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm" style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal);">✓ You're done holding it together with memory and duct tape</p>
                    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); margin: var(--space-3) 0;" />
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">If you're a startup still figuring out what you do, this isn't the right time. Come back when you've got demand and need a system.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 5 — GUARANTEE -->
    <section class="section section--statement section--padded surface-base">
        <div class="grid-page">
            <div class="col-content stack-6 text-center">
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section" style="margin-inline: auto;">
                    WE DON'T PROMISE YOU'LL GET RICH.<br />
                    <span class="t-accent t-flicker">WE PROMISE THE SYSTEM GETS BUILT.</span>
                </h2>
                <div class="stack-2" style="max-width: 50ch; margin-inline: auto; text-align: left;">
                    <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">✓ Fully built and installed lead system</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">✓ Tested capture and routing</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">✓ Verified automations that actually fire</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">✓ Working dashboard you can check from your phone</p>
                </div>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">
                    If we don't deliver what we said, we fix it. No bullshit. No "well, technically..."
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section section--cta section--padded section--mic-drop has-scanlines" style="position: relative;">
        <div class="grid-page" style="position: relative; z-index: 2;">
            <div class="col-content text-center stack-4">
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section" style="color: #fff; margin-inline: auto;">
                    READY TO STOP<br />
                    <span class="mic-drop__headline">DUCT-TAPING IT?</span>
                </h2>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-4); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: var(--space-4);">
                    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--lg">Apply to Install Your System →</a>
                    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--lg btn--mic-outline">Got Questions? Let's Talk</a>
                </div>
                <p style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.8rem; color: #ffffff; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-top: var(--space-3);">
                    Takes 5 minutes. We review it in 48 hours. No pitch on the first call.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</BaseLayout>
